<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM3.5">
<l>kālaik katuviṭu kiṉṟa kayalōṭu vāḷai viravi</l>
<l>vēlaip piṭitteṉṉai mārka ḷōṭṭi leṉṉa viḷaiyāṭṭō</l>
<l>kōlac ciṟṟāṭai palavuṅ koṇṭunī yēṟi yirātē</l>
<l>kōlaṅ kariya pirāṉē kuruntiṭaik kūṟai paṇiyāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The scabbard-fish and the carp are stinging [our] feet together!</l>
<l>If my brothers chase [You] away carrying lances, what [sort of] fun would [that] be?</l>
<l>Do not remain atop [the tree] seizing [our] many pretty small garments!</l>
<l>Do give [back] the clothes that are on the wild lime tree, O dark-bodied Lord!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
